WEBVTT

00:09:29.911 --> 00:09:34.024
And at these festivals there would be
some other gloomy writers,

00:09:34.048 --> 00:09:38.967
and they would come from places
such as Egypt, Nigeria, Pakistan,

00:09:38.991 --> 00:09:43.457
Bangladesh, Philippines,
China, Venezuela, Russia.

00:09:44.036 --> 00:09:46.389
And we would smile
at each other in sympathy,

00:09:46.413 --> 00:09:48.510
this camaraderie of the doomed.

00:09:48.534 --> 00:09:50.276
(Laughter)

00:09:51.165 --> 00:09:53.369
And you could call us WADWIC:

00:09:53.393 --> 00:09:57.511
Worried and Depressed
Writers International Club.

00:09:57.535 --> 00:09:59.257
(Laughter)

00:09:59.281 --> 00:10:01.052
But then things began to change,